{"title":"天平系统2","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2866","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">一个天平，砝码分别为</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">1g</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">3g</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">9g</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">、</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">27g</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">、</span><span style=\"\">...<span style=\"\">、</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">6561g</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Courier New';\">，每个砝码只有一个，要称重的物品放在天平的左侧，而砝码允许放在天平的左右两侧。已知一个物品的重量，问如何称重？试编程解决。</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">一个重量N</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p class=\"p0\" style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: '宋体'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes';\">所使用的砝码重量，按从大到小的顺序输出。其中与物品异侧的砝码用正号表示，与物品同侧的砝码用负号表示。（第一个砝码前的正号要省略）</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>15</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">27-9-3</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">（1≤N≤10000）</span></p>\n<!--EndFragment-->\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}